Title: If God Invited You to a Party
---
If God invited you to a party and said,
"Everyone in the ballroom tonight will be my special guest,"
how would you then treat them when you arrived? Indeed, indeed!
And Hafiz knows there is no one in this world who is not standing upon His
jeweled dance floor.
